graph TD
    User(Remote User) -->|UDP 1194| Gateway(Node A: OpenVPN)
    Gateway -->|DNS Queries| PiHole(Pi-Hole DNS)
    Gateway -->|Reverse Proxy| NPM(Nginx Proxy Manager)
    
    subgraph "Internal Network (192.168.1.x)"
        NPM -->|HTTP| Gitea(Gitea Git Server)
        NPM -->|HTTP| Jellyfin(Jellyfin Media)
        NPM -->|HTTP| Kasm(Kasm VDI)
        
        Jellyfin -->|Mount| Storage(Node C: 1TB HDD)
        Nextcloud -->|Mount| Storage
    end
    
    subgraph "Hardware Layer"
        NodeA[Node A: Gateway]
        NodeB[Node B: AI/Compute]
        NodeC[Node C: Storage]
        NodeD[Node D: Worker]
    end
